HEADWORD: Dendroidal
<hw>Den*droid"al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ treelike;
<grk>de`ndron</grk> tree + <grk>e'i^dos</grk> form: cf. F.
<ets>dendro⟦ium⟧de</ets>.]</ety> <def>Resembling a shrub or tree in
form; treelike; branching.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> arboreal, arboreous, arborescent, arboresque,
arboriform, dendriform, treelike, tree-shaped.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

